snippet.title: Parcel Corps - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX x Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Check out the latest fun trailer for Parcel Corps, featuring a moving speech about freelance bicycle messengers from Wallaby Wheelers CEO Bruce Crooke. The trailer also showcases gameplay and a new location from the upcoming extreme sports game coming to PS5, Xbox Series X/S, and PC in 2024.
